channel.description: I'm using a blank source, Teleports don't actually teleport, So where do i put the co-ords? thanks.

item.title: [317]Teleports
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

Purely Pink:

Well, it all depends on the source. For a delta, the coords go under the teleport’s case in clickingMost.Java

DeltaScape isn’t a base, it’s merely yet another server with a few methods refactored, which isn’t hard to do at all.

@Author:
Find the teleports packet ID, then add it into the switch statement inside packet 185, and add the teleport into that packet, if you don’t already have a teleport method then i suggest you search moparscape for one, someone is bound to of already posted.
